desert hawk gold corp
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Materials
Industry: Metals & Mining
Sub-Industry: Precious Metal Mining
Desert Hawk Gold Corporation provides mining services. The Company acquires, explores, and develops mineral and metal mining projects and produces gold, silver, copper, tungsten, molybdenum, lead, and zinc. Desert Hawk Gold Corp operates in the Western United States.




