July 22, 2017 12:08 PM ET
Metals and Mining

Company Overview of Desert Hawk Gold Corp.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Desert Hawk Gold Corp., an exploration stage company, explores for and develops mineral properties in the United States. The company primarily explores for gold and silver deposits from its Kiewit property. It holds interests in 247 unpatented mining claims, 42 patented claims, and 3 Utah state mineral leases that cover an area of approximately 25 square miles located in the Gold Hill Mining District in Tooele County, Utah. The company was formerly known as Lucky Joe Mining Company and changed its name to Desert Hawk Gold Corp. in April 2009. Desert Hawk Gold Corp. was incorporated in 1957 and is based in Reno, Nevada.


1290 Holcomb AvenueReno, NV 89502United StatesFounded in 195718 Employees



Phone: 775-337-8057








